Description:
A Scaffold Education surgiu da necessidade educacional como chave para mudar o mundo. Unindo tecnologia e educação, encontramos através de soluções estratégicas uma maneira de proporcionar experiências de aprendizagem personalizadas de acordo com as necessidades de cada pessoa, visando seu crescimento profissional e pessoal.

Nosso objetivo é aumentar os resultados das organizações através do desenvolvimento humano!

Nossos produtos e serviços:

Plataforma Scaffold de Gestão da Aprendizagem;
Produção de Conteúdo;
Consultoria Pedagógica;
Curadoria de Conteúdo;

TWYN is a 5-year-old company with global ambitions.

TWYN is revolutionizing digital interaction. With the oversaturation of social media, digital experiences can often feel passive, empty, shallow, and impersonal. Twyn will empower millions of face-to-face connections through technology that feels real and unique to everyone. And we're starting with the digital scaling of humans. One human in particular: The GOAT, Lionel Messi.
Some of our key achievements:
· We have signed a B2B contract we expect to be worth $100m + over the next 24 – 36 months, which should deliver profitability from H1 2023;
· We have secured a US Patent for a key aspect of our technology;
· Our B2B contract is with the Lionel Messi Brand and involves ten other global icons - giving our technology a global platform, reaching his 500m+ followers as well as the wider sports and entertainment markets;
· Our technology already powers two beta applications that, as at April 2023 have received over 400,000 downloads since their launch in May last year;
· Our team have been involved as founders or co-founders in over 20 start-ups, delivering returns exceeding $1 billion on invested equity of c. $100m;
· We expect the market size of interactive conversational media to reach the trillions over the next decade and we are well positioned to be leaders in that space.

HOLYWATER is a global tech company reshaping entertainment by unlocking creators' potential with AI and smart technology. With over 85 million users and 100 million hours of streamed content, HOLYWATER is redefining how stories are told and experienced.

HOLYWATER empowers creators to produce, distribute, and monetize their work in a fair, streamlined way—bringing original stories to millions of users across the globe.

HOLYWATER’s product portfolio includes:
– My Drama, the #1 vertical series platform among US and European companies, delivering bite-sized series for fast-paced lives;
– My Passion, a top-2 e-book platform in the niche;
– My Muse, an interactive, AI-powered streaming platform redefining storytelling;
– Freebits, an ad-supported vertical streaming service offering premium content for free.

Founded in 2020 by visionary entrepreneurs, HOLYWATER started as a 7-person startup and has since grown into a global team of over 200 specialists. Born in Ukraine, the company now operates across multiple countries.

HOLYWATER’s innovations have been featured by Forbes US and TechCrunch as examples of how technology is transforming the future of entertainment. In 2025, the company’s AI short film The Distance Between Two Points of Me received two Gold Telly Awards and was named an Honoree at the Runway AI Film Festival. My Drama also won a Webby Award People’s Voice for Best Streaming Service.

In the same year, Sifted (backed by the Financial Times) included HOLYWATER in its list of the fastest-growing companies in Europe.

